title: HiddenInSubscribeeCol
pid: 62e2bf29-fd04-4070-83ea-165b8aef62d7
body: |2-
  - set update
  - goal list is strange, but the name spells it out:
    each member is in its grandparent and hidden from its great-grandparent
  - children it creates, indefinitive, need no updating
  - lying members become independent
  - unusually, deletes itself if it finds itself empty
